Beautiful ❤️ From Sabri Brothers to Atif Aslam, this is my favorite naat to date. ❤ Amazing lyrics. Those who know Urdu, Arabic, Persian  languages know that these words are so precious. They go above and beyond to describe our beloved Prophet Muhammad Sallallahu Alayhi Wasallam beautifully. ❤

Love and prayers from Europe. ❤
Salaam (peace) to everybody out there listening to this masterpiece!
